@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000
@userA = 11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111
@userB = 22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222
@characterId = 00000000-0000-0000-0000-000000000000

### 0) Seed dữ liệu demo
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/dev/seed

### 1) Lấy danh sách user
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users

### 2) Quay gacha
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/gacha/pull
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{userA}}",
  "bannerTag": "season1-global",
  "cost": 160,
  "idempotencyKey": "pull-001"
}

### 3) Xem roster user
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/roster/{{userA}}

### 4) Xem pool hiếm còn lại
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/pool/live?minRarity=8

### 5) Đánh trận (đổi characterId theo roster)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/battle/fight
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{userA}}",
  "characterId": "{{characterId}}",
  "difficulty": "hard"
}

### 6) Hồi sinh bằng Soul Stone
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/roster/{{characterId}}/revive
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": "{{userA}}",
  "consumeSoulStone": true
}

### 7) Finalize permadeath
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/internal/permadeath/finalize
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nowUtc": "2026-04-17T00:00:00Z"
}
